data.name: qlfctn_subject_id.LookupColumns
data.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"?> <Root LookupSqlQuery="SELECT	QS.qlfctn_subject_id,QS.qlfctn_subject_nm, QS.qlfctn_subject_cd	
FROM	CDB..qlfctn_subjects QS
LEFT OUTER JOIN	CDB..qualifications_qlfctn_subjects QQS	ON	QS.qlfctn_subject_id	=	QQS.qlfctn_subject_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN	CDB..qualifications Q ON	QQS.qualification_id	=	Q.qualification_id
WHERE	Q.Qualification_nm = '%qualification_nm%' And ?"> <LookupColumn caption="Qlfctn Subject Id" sqlName="qlfctn_subject_id" aliasName="qlfctn_subject_id" percentageWidth="20" toolTipText="Qlfctn Subject Id" isDisplayMemberColumn="False" isValueMemberColumn="True" isCodeMemberColumn="False" tablePrefix="QS" /> <LookupColumn caption="Qlfctn Subject Code" sqlName="qlfctn_subject_cd" aliasName="qlfctn_subject_cd" percentageWidth="20" toolTipText="Qlfctn Subject Code" isDisplayMemberColumn="False" isValueMemberColumn="False" isCodeMemberColumn="True" tablePrefix="QS" /> <LookupColumn caption="Qlfctn Subject Name" sqlName="qlfctn_subject_nm" aliasName="qlfctn_subject_nm" percentageWidth="60" toolTipText="Qlfctn Subject Name" isDisplayMemberColumn="True" isValueMemberColumn="False" isCodeMemberColumn="False" tablePrefix="QS" /> </Root>
